  "original_code": "\ndef maxXORInRange(L, R): \n\n\tLXR = L ^ R \n\tmsbPos = 0\n\twhile(LXR): \n\t\n\t\tmsbPos += 1\n\t\tLXR >>= 1\n\tmaxXOR, two = 0, 1\n\t\n\twhile (msbPos): \n\t\n\t\tmaxXOR += two \n\t\ttwo <<= 1\n\t\tmsbPos -= 1\n\n\treturn maxXOR \n\nL, R = [int(i) for i in input().split()]\nprint(maxXORInRange(L, R)) \n\n",
